  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Headphone Automate</strong> is a paid application developed by [Your Name/Company]. 
     This SERVICE is provided as a one-time purchase app and is intended for use as is.</p>

  <h2>Information Collection and Use</h2>
  <p>Headphone Automate does not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable information 
     (such as name, email, phone number, or location).</p>

  <h2>Permissions</h2>
  <p>The permissions requested by this app are used strictly to enable its features:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Bluetooth</strong>: To detect and manage connected headphones or other audio devices. No data is stored or shared.</li>
    <li><strong>Notifications</strong>: To display alerts and updates about headphone connection status or app activity.</li>
    <li><strong>Overlay (System Alert Window)</strong>: To show floating widgets on the screen, only if enabled by the user.</li>
    <li><strong>Foreground Service</strong>: To keep headphone automation features running in the background when required.</li>
    <li><strong>Audio/Media</strong>: To mute or adjust sound automatically when headphones are connected or disconnected.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Payment</h2>
  <p>This is a paid app. Google Play Store manages the purchase process. 
     We do not collect or store your payment details. Any payment information is handled securely by Google Play in accordance with its policies.</p>

  <h2>Data Retention</h2>
  <p>Since this app does not collect any personal data, no information is stored or retained.</p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>This app does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking SDKs.</p>

  <h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
  <p>This app is not directed at children under the age of 13. As no personal data is collected, there is no risk to children’s data.</p>

  <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any updates will be reflected on this page. 
     Users are encouraged to review this page periodically for changes.</p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
